<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">1 - As a leader be clear on what you want<br/>2 - Effectively get it done from other people<br/><br/>The rest of the book is simply about how to get the above two po<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">1 - As a leader be clear on what you want<br />2 - Effectively get it done from other people<br /><br />The rest of the book is simply about how to get the above two points done. Finally, you need immense courage to pull it off.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
